query:
SELECT id AS "id: Id<Races>" FROM races WHERE
                series = $1
                AND event = $2
                AND phase = $3
                AND round = $4
                AND game = $5
                AND team1 = $6
                AND team2 = $7
                AND team3 = $8
                AND p1 = $9
                AND p2 = $10
                AND p3 = $11
                AND p1_discord = $12
                AND p2_discord = $13
                AND p1_twitch = $14
                AND p2_twitch = $15
                AND total = $16
                AND finished = $17
